It sounds like a lighthearted song and whenever I listened to it I found myself smiling and tapping my feet joyfully. But it's a sad song about a love ending, "I don't love you anymore"...Is it true? Mmm...I don't know. But I do know that I love TY and his songs/MVs ever and ever more...This video is a treat for us. Let's taste it more and more...
